Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜的生祭就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事終將超越時空
