Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非非非  非常讓人感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我也算是比較在意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  各位小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吞口水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人緊張的瞬間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷  雷斯塔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  翻！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我記得是不小心滑倒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼大家會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼…
