Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡扯什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夜襲啊
