Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷姆的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然越看越覺得厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  格雷姆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…你看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著這個也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是自動人偶卻能自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又聽得懂人話  還偶爾能說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聲音實在太大了點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想分解了看一下裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你眼神好可怕啊阿尼艾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流流流  流口水了你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的是好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像裡面有個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探戈  你剛才說什麼來著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  就像裡面有個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  一定有人在格雷姆裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  這樣就能解開所有的謎題了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰啊  格雷姆裡面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那軀體上來看應該是  尼克？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個健美的身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是納剛大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音非常相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似的可不只是聲音而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:19:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  那細心體貼的態度難道說是雷斯塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說還是說  出人意料的阿貝哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中還要熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿貝哥  太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  可怕的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷姆  差不多到定期檢修的時間了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也辛苦你了  格雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  關好門窗了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯就拜託姐姐做了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就讓我一起檢修一次格雷姆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐請優先新娘修行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊做晚飯  一邊等著工作歸來的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這能成為一個很好的練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真不錯啊  薩爾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  親  愛  的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼格雷姆  就像往常一樣開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷姆的真身終於要暴露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快變回來吧  阿尼艾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吧  可以脫了哦  格雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼天花板上挺熱鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  一會再告訴姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進行檢修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真不錯啊  薩爾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  親  愛  的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常棒  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有什麼能教你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來今天進行大檢修了嗎？我聽到些大聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了  那聲音是從天花板上傳來的哦  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天  天花板上？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在慌什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我才不知道姐姐三更半夜在觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:22:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板上那些雷斯塔的猥瑣周邊物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「用」雷斯塔的周邊物…才正確答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說八道什麼啊莉特絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Campanella殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉自由行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次介紹的溫泉是在龍的世界盡頭的龍之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對色塊  麻花臉  皮膚乾燥  還有皮膚褶皺非常有效
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺必死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這溫泉對像我們這樣皮膚嫩滑的女孩來說是不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找切露西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在畫面中的某個地方裡隱藏著切露小姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道是在哪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制10秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:23:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會輸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,0:24:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀  石頭  布
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You Lose
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我贏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先叫雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.24,0:24:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這社會可不是那麼好混的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔變成布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉  在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦米澤  真是貴客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.76,0:24:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我在旅行時遇到的古代遺跡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了個有趣的聖者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.83,0:24:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你和觀眾的各位應該會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣  然後這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是挺有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.28,0:24:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.97,0:24:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.01,0:25:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.72,0:25:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我的眼睛！眼睛～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.92,0:25:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.66,0:25:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這是誰忘拿了的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.29,0:25:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.31,0:25:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.85,0:25:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.73,0:25:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連細節都做得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.36,0:26:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連…細節都…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.09,0:26:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這裡也洗白白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.45,0:26:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊  好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.56,0:26:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  慢慢享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.51,0:26:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸果然還是比較喜歡卡莉娜啊切露西那樣大大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.75,0:26:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.49,0:26:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…最喜歡你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.45,0:27:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是說弄丟了嗎  那個布偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.41,0:27:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我早上起來就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.47,0:27:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來雷斯塔  你昨晚到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.68,0:27:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？…稍微有點事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.60,0:27:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.76,0:27:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.84,0:27:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.38,0:27:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.11,0:27:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.88,0:27:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是發燒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.30,0:27:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  把額頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.22,0:27:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  看來太刺激了
